中文課程簡介


介紹各類不同功能的化妝品，包化妝品的成分及作用，瞭解並學習如何選擇合適、安全的化妝品，並實作學習自製環保化妝品。




英文課程簡介


This course introduces all kinds of cosmetics, including the
  composition and function of cosmetics, understand and learn how to choose the
  right, safe cosmetics, and practice to learn self-made green cosmetics.




