(英文) The Lifetime and Science
  Technology




授課教師


李振偉


(學歷) 國立中山大學資工博士




使用教材


主要教材：自編講義教學




中文課程簡介


「科技與人生」希望能成為一門實用的課程，能讓e世代的大學生對應用科技邏輯於人生各方面有初步瞭解，另一方面，面對現在許多聰明但學生動機可能並不夠強的學生們，本課程設計老師們希望教學內容對學生而言能有趣而具挑戰性的。課程內容包括生活科技中基本通信原理與應用、快速進行中的全球暖化以及全球暖化的影響與因應之道。課程中將穿插影片欣賞使同學感受另一種傳達訊息與理念的方式，並且也以分組口頭報告的方式，讓同學個別進行資料蒐集與相互討論，以便達到互相砥礪的作用。




英文課程簡介


"The Lifetime and Science Technology"
  wants to be a practical course that allows e-generation students having a
  preliminary understanding for the application of technology in all aspects of
  life. On the other hand, for some intelligent students who may not be strong
  enough motivation to learn, the course is designed for teachers who want
  students to the teaching content interesting and challenging. Topics will
  include basic life science, technology in communication theory, the impact of
  global warming and how to face the global warming. Course will enable
  students to appreciate the movie which provide another way to convey
  information and ideas to the students. We also apply group oral presentation,
  which allows students to collect data and individaul discussions with each
  other to achieve the role of temper with each other.




授課方式


課堂講述及分組討論報告




